       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CLOSPEN1.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
      * CARD ACCOUNT CLOSURE PENALTY CALCULATON
      * REF: MASTER DIRECTION 2022 PARA 8(A) - PENALTY OF RS 500 PER
      * DAY OF DELAY BEYOND SEVEN WORKING DAYS FROM CLOSURE REQUEST.
      * BUSINESS RULE: PENALTY ACCRUES ON WORKING DAYS ONLY, AS
      * PENALTY IS PER DAY AND SLA ITSELF IS IN WORKING DAYS.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-INPUTS.
           05  WS-ELAPSED-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-WEEKEND-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-WORK-AREAS.
           05  WS-WORKING-DAYS       PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-DELAY-DAYS         PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY-AMT        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PEN-RATE           PIC 9(3) VALUE 500.
           05  WS-SLA-DAYS           PIC 9(2) VALUE 7.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-WEEKEND-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS
           PERFORM 2000-COMPUTE-PENALTY
           DISPLAY 'PENALTY: ' WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       2000-COMPUTE-PENALTY.
           COMPUTE WS-WORKING-DAYS = WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
                   - WS-WEEKEND-DAYS - WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS
           COMPUTE WS-DELAY-DAYS = WS-WORKING-DAYS - WS-SLA-DAYS
           IF WS-DELAY-DAYS > ZERO
              COMPUTE WS-PENALTY-AMT = WS-PEN-RATE * WS-DELAY-DAYS
           ELSE
              MOVE ZERO TO WS-PENALTY-AMT
           END-IF.
